-- Honda U.S. sales down 3.2 percent in July
-- 
-- Wed Aug 1, 2007 2:27pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/01/us-honda-sales-us-idUSWNAS925020070801

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Honda Motor Co Ltd ( 7267.T ) on Wednesday said its U.S. sales fell an adjusted 3.2 percent in July. 

 The Japanese automaker said it sold 141,049 vehicles in the United States in July, including results for its luxury Acura brand. That compared with 151,804 vehicles a year earlier. The percentage change in Honda results was adjusted for an extra selling day in July last year compared with the same month a year earlier.